âœ… **Drag & Drop**: React Beautiful DND integration for intuitive task management

âœ… **CRUD Operations**: Comprehensive task service with filtering and pagination

âœ… **Role-Based Access**: Granular permission system for secure operations

âœ… **Form Validation**: Yup schemas for robust data validation

âœ… **Performance**: Optimized rendering with React.memo and useMemo

âœ… **Accessibility**: Proper ARIA labels and keyboard navigation support

